thread.title: Strange late sequence gives Seattle 13-10 win over Detroit
thread.title_full: Strange late sequence gives Seattle 13-10 win over Detroit

title: Strange late sequence gives Seattle 13-10 win over Detroit
text:
> Sports Strange late sequence gives Seattle 13-10 win over Detroit Seattle Seahawks strong safety Kam Chancellor (31) knocks the ball loose from Detroit Lions wide receiver Calvin Johnson (81) in the second half of an NFL football game, Monday, Oct. 5, 2015, in Seattle. The fumble went out of bounds in the end zone and was ruled a touchback. The Seahawks beat the Lions 13-10. (AP Photo/Elaine Thompson)
